284
00:20:14,360 --> 00:20:15,440
Bar?

285
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:16,840
Xia Lin?

286
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:41,920
Hello?

287
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:44,160
<i>Are you Yao Liang's sister?</i>

288
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,800
If you didn't reject Yao Liang that day,

289
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,800
he wouldn't go looking for you at the bar.

290
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:57,240
If he didn't witness the two of you meet,

291
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:59,320
he wouldn't get drunk
and get into an accident.

292
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:00,800
And you?

293
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:04,280
You don't even know
what Yao Liang did for you.

294
00:21:04,560 --> 00:21:06,840
You've just been
enjoying your life guilt-free.

295
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:09,280
Enjoying all the attention and praise.

296
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:10,840
Enjoying love and everything.

297
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,680
You've been living
the life of an innocent person,

298
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:13,760
but what about him?

299
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,080
He's still in the hospital.

300
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:18,880
My mom cries every day.

301
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,480
And me?

302
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:24,280
I had to quit my job and start over.

303
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:27,560
I had to see the person
who caused my family pain every day.

304
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:29,840
Not just one,

305
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:32,040
but two.

306
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:35,040
You became my manager

307
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:37,720
one year ago,

308
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:41,520
just so you could avenge your brother?

309
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,600
You ruined his life.

310
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,120
You took everything from him.

311
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:48,080
Of course I had to do something.

312
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,600
Didn't you want to be a movie star?

313
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:51,920
Sure.

314
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:54,040
That's why I helped manage your career

315
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:55,960
and brought you a lot of attention.

316
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:58,280
Once you get used to the vanity,

317
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:01,440
