any new treatments to cure him.

357
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,840
Medicine is so advanced nowadays.

358
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:55,760
He might have a chance to wake up.

359
00:24:58,600 --> 00:24:59,760
Thank you.

360
