You're so kind, Mr. Ling.

361
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:09,360
That's because I married
such a good-looking and kind woman.

362
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:13,600
I held the party

363
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:16,040
to give you a surprise.

364
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:18,520
I didn't expect

365
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:21,480
that all this would happen.

366
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,560
It's fine.

367
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:24,000
That's not important.

368
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:28,760
Meeting you was the best thing
that ever happened to me.

369
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:30,360
I didn't know that

370
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:32,880
