-Right?

535
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:39,080
-Yes.
-So nice.

536
00:35:45,720 --> 00:35:46,960
<i>Hello? Chu Yan.</i>

537
00:35:47,040 --> 00:35:48,240
I'm sorry.

538
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:50,480
I just thought that was a nice photo.

539
00:35:51,040 --> 00:35:53,360
I didn't mean to...

540
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,320
I know.

541
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:02,200
Sorry about all the trouble.

542
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:04,520
It's fine.

543
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:05,760
Don't worry about it.

544
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,840
I'll just post on Sohu Friends

545
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,880
<i>that my girlfriend is Bojue Photography.</i>

546
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:12,840
<i>It'll be an advertising opportunity.</i>

547
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:15,560
Chu Yan, I actually...

