00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:07,120
Will you get some for me?

638
00:41:07,960 --> 00:41:10,280
Feifei, next time you get your period,

639
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,800
-I'll get some for you.
-Okay, stop talking.

640
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:24,440
Boss, Mrs. Ling is holding a party.

641
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:26,200
-Really?
-Yes.

642
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:28,320
Look.

643
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:31,160
My Mumu is preparing a surprise for me.

644
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:32,840
Are you jealous?

645
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:37,120
Feifei has prepared surprises
for me before.

646
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:40,360
Really?

647
00:41:48,600 --> 00:41:49,600
Hello, Feifei.

648
00:41:49,680 --> 00:41:51,080
Can I talk to you about something?

649
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:52,240
<i>What is it?</i>

650
00:41:53,720 --> 00:41:54,640
Could you...

651
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:57,840
prepare a surprise for me?

652
00:43:28,920 --> 00:43:29,840
I'm telling you.

653
00:43:29,920 --> 00:43:31,480
You can't be an irresponsible man.

654
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:33,040
-Dad.
-Dad!

655
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:36,960
I mean, Mr. Chu.

656
00:43:38,800 --> 00:43:40,600
Chu Yan, I like you.

657
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:43,880
Get out!

